Package: foldcluster
Title: Fusing of Localized Densities: a Bayesian clustering method 
  for misspecified models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Alexander Dombowsky
Maintainer: The package maintainer <alexander.dombowsky@duke.edu>
Description: This package contains the functions required to implement the 
  FOLD clustering method for Bayesian Gaussian mixture models as described in
  Dombowsky and Dunson (2023+). "Bayesian Clustering via Fusing of 
  Localized Densities".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
